docs {
  ## Patch Recipe Equipment
  อัปเดตบางฟิลด์ของอุปกรณ์ทำอาหารโดยไม่แทนที่ข้อมูลทั้งหมด

  Partially updates specific fields of a kitchen equipment definition without replacing the entire record.


  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "name": "",
    "is_active": true
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

